# Related Article in Blogger
This plugin can be used on single post.
It shows posts by the first label of the post.
To use it, need the HTML structure below:
> <div id='related-article' expr:data-label='data:post.labels.first.name' expr:data-url='data:post.url.canonical'><script src='//chengkai505.github.io/Blogger-Plugins/Related-Article/main.js'/><h4>相關文章</h4></div>